title: TUESDAY 2/23 - Cam Newton isn't done yet
itunes:title: TUESDAY 2/23 - Cam Newton isn't done yet
description:
Cam Newton explains "The Patriot Way" and why he isn't going to hang up his cleats just yet. Carson Wentz may be on his way to Indianapolis, but second-year wideout Michael Pittman Jr. isn't giving up his number 11 jersey. Packers running back Jamaal Williams explains why he wants to be a Packer for life. Jacksonville plans on declining the option on Tyler Eifert. Steelers restructure Cam Heyward's contract t to create cap space. Mike Tomlin tests positive for Covid-19 and remains away from the Steelers facility.
